nodes.text: Corey Dee Williams (born August 14, 1960) is the son of Billy Dee Williams, who played Lando Calrissian in the Star Wars original trilogy. Corey played the character Klaatu during the scenes on Jabba's Sail Barge and also doubled for his father as Calrissian in the 1983 film Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi.
